                     </persName>
                  , widow, commonly called Dowager Lady Temple, one trunk, value 10 s.; three coats, value 8 l.; two waistcoats, value 1 l.; three pair of breeches, value 30 s., and two 10 l. Bank notes, the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18211024-125-victim1155" type="victimName">
                           Thomas 
                           Baker
